abstract: Samantha Stosur beats Sloane Stephens to reach finals at Strasbourg International; other tennis news noted.
lead_paragraph: Stosur defeated Sloane Stephens, 6-3, 3-6, 6-0, and was to meet Kristina Mladenovic in the title match.

headline.main: Samantha Stosur Reaches Final at Strasbourg International
